{"tid":998873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[請勿中伏]首都廣場間娃娃星球 同 香港郵意係同一個老闆！","createTime":"2019-01-28T09:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:57:51.000Z","uid":1181,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"28483586c5cc195f3663020614084416de9cfcb2","tid":998873,"uid":1181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n[借連登上位]尖沙咀夾公仔機老闆可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/948735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/948735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">娃娃星球</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4Ynaib.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4Ynaib.png&h=e58408ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近呢間野搵咗出軌老婦人宣傳間夾公仔鋪<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>順便</strong></span>介紹埋隔離間香港郵意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBks5TN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBks5TN.png&h=a542d155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多位得閪閒既巴絲千其唔好走去打搞人地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14zhJGV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14zhJGV.png&h=5d7283b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n員工有志氣 屌人咪屌人 話知你唱錢定唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港郵意</span></strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我係一個前food blogger，有啲餐廳真係當啲客係狗2（香港郵意七宗罪）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/949326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/949326</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n可能有啲巴絲唔知香港郵意做乜會俾人屌，重溫一下呢間野既經典事蹟！<br />\n<br />\n1: 食屙人！<br />\n//二、食品安全問題<br />\n上post少少更新，樓主同一齊食火鍋嘅fd返屋企後相繼感到不適，兩人均有腹瀉症狀，醫生確診為食物中毒。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVeJEhn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVeJEhn.png&h=61b4174e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Va7bOaT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVa7bOaT.png&h=b943fbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2: 員工態度差、係Facebook公然屌客<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MptQp1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MptQp1.png&h=7854ba0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfvs5Yn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftfvs5Yn.png&h=4c0b9925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有更多事蹟歡迎大家追Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5265b2f3bc962e1e30bdb652988b1feb2441616","tid":998873,"uid":1181,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fB1cxFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfB1cxFe.png&h=174ac7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現代創業奇材Ivan囝<br />\n全港第一間員工可以瘋狂屌客既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f1cfb3b315936a086c41a6dd048874c0ccea76","tid":998873,"uid":12264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:01:17.000Z","msg":"一早知，間夾公仔D人D場主都係態度串過狗<br />\n佢想借夾公仔黎整旺埋個場姐<br />\n如果佢個場淨做餐廳??食屎吧啦<br />\n全部員工當全部客係西客<br />\n完全無諗過自己係最西個個<br />\n連基本餐廳員工要有既禮貌都無，仲想人唔西你面?"},{"pid":"4f00562a38d23976b3935192f573260678d8c743","tid":998873,"uid":1181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286ffeeb7c87faed6fa732c5c74c558a88f39556","tid":998873,"uid":182538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5795c308399fa7d24c7aade761caf6073764f9","tid":998873,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母呢間閪野幫襯過 慶撚過火屎<br />\n我都開post講過"},{"pid":"b01e10256d5e38d21dee35f14366fe3807a1e91f","tid":998873,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57568bd26c15b79c29758dc5d3eb2098d6be06d5","tid":998873,"uid":1181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c00db8637736e66bc9f2f744d7652b27c376d02","tid":998873,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"支持Miss Pun<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_15.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_15.gif&h=6860f8c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98244ebe31ea410d55b7c2ce21519c1d638e54e0","tid":998873,"uid":86246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味呢間我夾左幾百蚊乜柒都夾唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD夾係會好快頂住同夾唔實"},{"pid":"4108d6845d52d7069f365f8472ede0bd4cdfb11d",